  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "So...what do you think? Do you want to get even stronger than you are right now? Pass a simple test and I can do just that for you...do you want to do it?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Good...you look strong, alright, but I need to see if it is for real. The test isn't terribly difficult, and you should be able to pass it. Here, take my letter first. Make sure you don't lose it."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Please get this letter to the #b#p319##k around #b#m10002070##k near #m10002000#. He's doing the role of an instructor in place of me ... "
        },
        "2": {
          "_dirName": "2",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Get him the letter and he'll test you in place of me. He'll give you all the details about it. Best of luck to you..."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Really? It will help you out a great deal on your journey if you get stronger fast...if you choose to change your mind in the future, please feel free to come back. Know that I'll make you much more powerful than you are right now..."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Hmmm... it is definitely the letter from #b#p313##k... so you came all the way here to take the test and make the 2nd job advancement as the magician?"
      }
    }
